headline: Q1 Earnings Roundup: Hershey (NYSE:HSY) And The Rest Of The Shelf-Stable Food Segment
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Hershey (NYSE:HSY) and the rest of the shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q1.
